cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CL. 

The paper deals with semantic segmentation, which is a computer vision task, hence cs.CV is the most likely category. The paper also proposes a new method for weakly supervised learning, which involves training a model with limited supervision, which falls under the category of machine learning, hence cs.LG and cs.AI are also likely categories. The paper also mentions the use of statistical information, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or natural language processing (cs.CL) categories.
